wiki.content: The song features American rapper B.O.B. Many collaborations find the two parties never actually meeting up but Jessie told MTV News she was determined that the pair would record the song whilst in the same room. "I didn't want it to be like, 'Do that, drop a bar and send it to me.' I wanted it to be an experience and a journey, so he wrote his bar and he flew to the U.K. to do the video," she said. "So, no green screen. We're there together. It was good fun. None of this, 'Never met him, don't know what he looks like.' I've proper been there, hugged him and smelled him."
